metadata.name: Leo Caillard - ARTEM Explosion
metadata.description:
The concept of this NFT is to connect the past and the present as I mainly do in most of my art creations. 

An ARTEM coin in high-speed motion explodes a classical statue. It's a meaningful representation of the "Virtuality" of the blockchain smashing the "Reality" of the past tangible world.

 It's also a dialog in between the past & the future that arise the question of the conservation of the Historical aspects of Humanbeing.
